You are here:

Marketing Cloud Intelligence

Get Customer Behavior Information with the LinkedIn Company Page Connector
Pull valuable information about user-generated posts when connecting to the LinkedIn API to learn more about your customers’ behavior, interests, and needs.

Leverage More Data from Google Display & Video 360
Analyze customer behavior data with additional fields, including data fees, full-screen selections, video mutes and unmutes, pauses, and skips.

Easily Integrate Marketing Cloud Intelligence with Google Search Ads 360
Take advantage of a more seamless integration with less implementation, and analyze more data with additional fields.

Drive Campaign Performance with Performance Max Data in Bing Ads
Pull in Performance Max campaign data with the Bing Ads API connector and analyze all your campaign data.
